Detailed Description

ITreeLine.

Description: The ITreeLine represents an actual line in a trace grid. The different cells are returned as QStrings through the [] operator or they can be extracted as a list by the toStringList function.

Limitations: This is an Interface style structure. It is not meant to be, and can not be instantiated. All subclasses must have the [] operator and toStringList overridden.
